subject: Cooperation with your company
description_text:
Hello!
My name is Maxim, I run my own Tik Tok channel on various computer
equipment, and have already managed to gather a good audience.
I would like to offer you cooperation on barter:
You send me any of your products, and I review them, release videos on my
channel, and perhaps arrange a draw among subscribers of my telegram
channel.
I would like to clarify that at the same time I indicate information about
you to everyone, make posts in the telegram, and mention you in videos
Here is my channel.
